oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Two men inspecting load of quail leaving Buffalo Springs State Game Farm in Grainger County, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of two men inspecting a load of quail ready to leave the Buffalo Springs State Game Farm near Rutledge, Tenn. The pickup truck is full of quail and in the background is more gaming farm equipment as well as a view of tree-lined ridges. One of the men is a farm worker wearing overalls and farm hat and the other a Tennessee Department of Conservation worker.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
